*.pkl
*.joblib
Save and close. Then run:

cmd
git add .gitignore
git add ml_pipeline/models/train.py
git add ml_pipeline/evaluation/metrics.py
cmd
git status
You should see all 3 files as green/staged. Then commit:

cmd
git commit -m "feat: add model training and evaluation scripts, fix gitignore"
cmd
git push origin main
Paste what you see! 🚀



